只能访问当前节点，当前节点不是末尾节点

借尸还魂：将当前节点的值和 next 全部更新为其 next，再删除 next

```cpp
void deleteNode(ListNode *node) {
    ListNode *next = node->next;
    node->val = next->val;    
    node->next = next->next;
    delete next;
}
```


